description:
As a merchant
  I want to create new delivery
  So that I can have different delivery for my shoppers
name: Third Party Delivery Create Feature

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct account email to email field
I fill correct account password to password field
I click on login button
I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button
I check intercom message notification frame and click intercom message close button
I check new feature alert notification frame and click new feature alert close button
I check and click exclude products panel close button
I check and click no thanks button
I am on Delivery Create Page
I select delivery type dropdown option included 'Store Pick-up' of delivery type dropdown
I fill "(dirty data) Store Pick-up" to name field
I select delivery fee type dropdown option included 'Flat Price' of delivery fee type dropdown
I click on select shipping countries link
I should see shipping zone settings popup
I click on select the rest of the world checkbox
I click on ok button
I should see upload button
I pick store address file to store address selector
uploaded address content should contain 'Upload File'

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"Upload File2 info of pick-up-store have been uploaded, of which 0 failed to upload.Please upload again, or ignore and save the uploaded data.","expectText":"Upload File"}

steps.name: I click on add button
I should see confirm adding button
I click on confirm adding button
I am on Delivery Options Page
1st row of delivery options list should contain "Store Pick-up"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"(dirty data) Store Pick-up Store Pick-up Flat Price Unpublish Edit Delete","expectText":"Store Pick-up"}

steps.name: I click on edit button of delivery method list
I should be redirected to Delivery Edit Page
I scroll down to update button
store preview list should contain "City"
store preview list should contain "Area"
store preview list should contain "District"
store preview list should contain "Address"
store preview list should contain "Pick-up-store Name"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"City Area District Address Pick-up-store Name","expectText":"Pick-up-store Name"}

steps.name: 1st store city preview should contain "Taipei City"
1st store area preview should contain "Da'an Dist."
1st store district preview should contain "Da'an Rd."
1st store address preview should contain "No. 100, Sec. 1, Da'an Rd.,"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"No. 100, Sec. 1, Da'an Rd.,","expectText":"No. 100, Sec. 1, Da'an Rd.,"}

steps.name: 1st store name preview should contain "Daan store 1"
2nd store city preview should contain "Taipei City"
2nd store area preview should contain "Da'an Dist."
2nd store district preview should contain "Da'an Rd."
2nd store address preview should contain "No. 666, Sec. 1, Da'an Rd.,"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"No. 666, Sec. 1, Da'an Rd.,","expectText":"No. 666, Sec. 1, Da'an Rd.,"}

steps.name: 2nd store name preview should contain "Daan store 2"
I should see upload button
---ROLL BACK---
I am on Delivery Options Page
I click delete button of delivery method list for the same order of row of delivery options list included 'dirty data'
I should see delete confirmation popover
I click on delete checkbox
I click on confirm delete button
table should not contain 'Store Pick-up'
